Convert a procedure with recursion:
```
// 4GL
procedure factorial(n = integer) = integer;
begin
    if n <= 1 then
        return 1;
    else
        return n * factorial(n - 1);
    endif;
end

// C#
public static int Factorial(int n)
{
    if (n <= 1)
    {
        return 1;
    }
    else
    {
        return n * Factorial(n - 1);
    }
}
```
